snippet.title: Ascend | REVEAL TRAILER
snippet.description:
Ascend is a first-person VR arena shooter with an immersive locomotion flight system. Rise to greatness by engaging in intense aerial combat!

Song: "Legendary" ft. composer Anthony Sabatino and guest rappers Jack Be and Martin.

Website: https://ascendtovictory.com/
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/ascendvr
Twitter: https://twitter.com/ascendvr
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/ascendvr/

Anthony Sabatino: http://www.anthonysabatinomusic.com/
Jackson Beavers: https://jack-be.com/
Martin: https://www.instagram.com/martin.2d/
